  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 2 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  delayBetweenCharacters: 0.1
  delayBetweenLines: 2
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - 'Just this morning, we have confirmed a second symptom that may appear as a result
    of the virus. '
  - Infected individuals experience severe back acne alongside the previously disclosed
    rash on the arm.
  - Any citizens who experience BOTH symptoms of back acne and a rash on the arm
    must contact us via their computer messaging application immediately.
  - Citizens who experience only 1 of 2 known symptoms are expected to not be infected,
    and will not need to contact anyone regarding this issue.
